
# the unix philosophy

1. do one thing and do it well
2. write programs that work together
3. use text for everything because that's the universal interface


## extrapolated

1. SRP, atomic operations.... limit the scope
2. make it composable
3. have good interfaces - interface > implementation


# categories of tools

- git status - listing files
- git diff - listing files
- git log - listing commits
- git root/master/sha/lb/rb - informational

# git status & git diff

cmd -> list of files

- status - changed but not commit
  - git status -s|--short
- diff - what files changed between 2 HEADs
  - git diff --name-only --relative


